00:09:44,430 --> 00:09:45,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

196
00:09:46,540 --> 00:09:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet he stood out, huh?</font>

197
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I mean, with his 
