00:11:25,590 --> 00:11:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad...</font>

231
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:31,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that you're both my friends.</font>

232
00:11:32,330 --> 00:11:34,170
