00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:42,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you did record
everything, but...</font>

340
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're adorable! They're so good!</i></font>

341
00:16:46,420 --> 00:16:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stop commenting on everything.</i></font>

342
00:16:49,920 --> 00:16:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They couldn't stop laughing.</font>

343
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

344
00:16:52,800 --> 00:16:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and when I was sorting through 
the photos from yesterday...</font>

345
00:16:59,370 --> 00:17:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why is Sero-kun
crying like that?</font>

346
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa, did you make him cry?</font>

347
00:17:04,360 --> 00:17:06,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he was moved
by your performance.</font>

348
00:17:07,260 --> 00:17:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

349
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:11,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like this picture!</font>

350
00:17:11,840 --> 00:17:12,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too!</font>

351
00:17:12,820 --> 00:17:14,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa, will you print it out?</font>

352
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put it in here and frame it!</font>

353
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:17,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frame it!</font>

354
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:19,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's weird to frame a photo
of someone who isn't family.</font>

355
00:17:19,650 --> 00:17:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it weird?</font>

356
00:17:20,790 --> 00:17:22,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine if it's weird!</font>

357
00:17:22,540 --> 00:17:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because Sero-kun is Sero-kun!</font>

358
00:17:25,810 --> 00:17:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why we have a
photo of you up at our place,</font>

359
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but now it's like I see you all day,
every day, and it makes me sick.</font>

360
00:17:32,810 --> 00:17:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, that's so mean!</font>

361
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to interrupt!</font>

362
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:41,450
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="8"><b><font color="#1e1d1d">Let's make sure to 
turn off the lights.</font></b></font></font>

363
00:17:41,450 --> 00:17:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, dear. What a scramble.</font>

364
00:17:47,860 --> 00:17:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fon-san, we don't have 
your part ready yet.</font>

365
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:52,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll wait!</font>

366
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still...</font>

367
00:17:56,090 --> 00:17:59,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's quite unusual for 
you all to be this busy.</font>

368
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way a well-informed 
guy like you doesn't know.</font>

369
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three nearby torture companies went bust,</font>

370
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and all their work came 
flooding to you, right?</font>

371
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's rare, but not unheard of.</font>

372
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:12,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you take on more cases?</font>

373
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:13,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know...</font>

374
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might be hard to take on any more.</font>

375
00:18:16,530 --> 00:18:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I do it? What do we have?</font>

376
00:18:18,950 --> 00:18:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One that'll be a pain,</font>

377
00:18:20,810 --> 00:18:22,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the other two are korokke cases.</font>

378
00:18:22,450 --> 00:18:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Please allow us to take those!</font>

379
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:24,410
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#f0f0f0">Sense of Justice</font></b></font></font>

380
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:24,410
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#f0f0f0">Spirit of Inquiry</font></b></font></font>

381
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're so reliable, aren't they?</font>

382
00:18:29,220 --> 00:18:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we're grateful.</font>

383
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:32,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take the rest!</font>

384
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The delivery dates for several 
of the cases have been adjusted!</font>

385
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

386
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which ones?</font>

387
00:18:40,420 --> 00:18:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These two... and the first ones 
that Siu-san is handling.</font>

388
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're pretty good! That's a huge help.</font>

389
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, this did happen really suddenly.</font>

390
00:18:49,120 --> 00:18:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm impressed you got 
an extension for this.</font>

391
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you convince them?</font>

392
00:18:52,670 --> 00:18:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said I had a Buddhist memorial 
service for a family member.</font>

393
00:18:55,870 --> 00:18:57,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this an after-school club?</font>

394
00:18:57,570 --> 00:18:59,990
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#303030">Let's build a <font color="#ea3574">fun, 
cheerful <font color="#303030">workplace together!</font></font></font></b></font>

395
00:18:57,570 --> 00:18:59,990
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#dffedf">Stop harassment!</font></b></font>

396
00:19:00,170 --> 00:19:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All that's left are Mike 
and Hugh's. I'll go tell them.</font>

397
00:19:03,410 --> 00:19:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll leave it to you. Also, hey...</font>

398
00:19:05,800 --> 00:19:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You reek.</font>

399
00:19:06,990 --> 00:19:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What'd you just say?!</font>

400
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, do your best, everyone!
I'll be waiting here.</font>

401
00:19:12,110 --> 00:19:13,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make yourself at home.</font>

402
00:19:13,690 --> 00:19:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you've got nothing to do, 
you could help us out, you know.</font>

403
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:19,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah. You used to do this 
a long time ago, right?</font>

404
00:19:19,390 --> 00:19:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Torture? I could never 
do something so uncivilized.</font>

405
00:19:24,060 --> 00:19:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way! No way! It's too scary!</font>

406
00:19:25,100 --> 00:19:28,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I don't want to hear that from 
someone who disposes of humans.</font>

407
00:19:29,270 --> 00:19:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone works so hard.</font>

408
00:19:31,510 --> 00:19:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You make good money from it, right?</font>

409
00:19:34,170 --> 00:19:35,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still...</font>

410
00:19:35,540 --> 00:19:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who'd have thought Spirytus 
would ever be this lively?</font>

411
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:41,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-kun, I'm happy for you.</font>

412
00:19:41,940 --> 00:19:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess.</font>

413
00:19:46,710 --> 00:19:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoo-hoo! I'm here!</font>

414
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you not act like you're 
my girlfriend when you come in?</font>

415
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:52,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you bored?</font>

416
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got pretty busy, huh?</font>

417
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:56,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

418
00:19:57,040 --> 00:20:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I asked the police to investigate 
an illegal torture company,</font>

419
00:20:00,330 --> 00:20:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they apparently found some others, too.</font>

420
00:20:02,780 --> 00:20:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On top of that, they asked me, 
"Your place is fine, right?"</font>

421
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:08,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How rude of them!</font>

422
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place is a gray that's 
as close to white it gets!</font>

423
00:20:10,600 --> 00:20:13,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're lily white, I'll have you know!</font>

424
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:16,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As someone who's known this 
place since you started it,</font>

425
00:20:16,700 --> 00:20:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spirytus has made me feel 
really emotional lately.</font>

426
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-kun and Sero-kun are 
as skilled as ever.</font>

427
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:23,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Done already?</font>

428
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm letting one sweat 
and working on another.</font>

429
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Same.</font>

430
00:20:25,780 --> 00:20:28,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike-chan and Hugh-kun have 
started to shape up nicely.</font>

431
00:20:25,780 --> 00:20:27,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Will you do this one with me?</font>

432
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:29,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Is it okay if I finish up this one first?</font>

433
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That's been changed, 
so we'll handle the arrangements.</font>

434
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:33,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Noe-chan seems like he's 
gotten used to everything.</font>

435
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:33,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes. Thank you for handling all that.</font>

436
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:36,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to come 
and torture here with us?</font>

437
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way! Not doing it!</font>

438
00:20:37,740 --> 00:20:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being a ragman suits me better!</font>

439
00:20:39,890 --> 00:20:42,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, you don't need anyone 
here who isn't fully devoted.</font>

440
00:20:43,730 --> 00:20:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spirytus is the best as it is right now!</font>

441
00:20:46,540 --> 00:20:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I suppose it is.</font>

442
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

443
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. You should 
deny it at least once!</font>

444
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm busy, too.</font>

445
00:20:54,710 --> 00:20:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go and do some work, would you?</font>

446
00:20:59,980 --> 00:21:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're done.</font>

447
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never knew things could get this busy.</font>

448
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just every once in a while.</font>

449
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once in a while...</font>

450
00:21:11,590 --> 00:21:13,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The deadline for my 
manuscript is coming up,</font>

451
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'm going to sleep 
like a log tonight!</font>

452
00:21:15,760 --> 00:21:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I think I'll do my 
assignment tomorrow.</font>

453
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When things like this happen, 
it makes a lot of other things harder.</font>

454
00:21:22,090 --> 00:21:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haven't you thought of quitting?</font>

455
00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:25,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Nope!</font>

456
00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:25,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not once!</font>

457
00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:25,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't.</font>

458
00:21:26,370 --> 00:21:28,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being able to be so useful to others...</font>

459
00:21:28,320 --> 00:21:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No other job is as 
worthwhile as this one!</font>

460
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there aren't many jobs 
that are this exciting.</font>

461
00:21:35,330 --> 00:21:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the first time I've found work 
that I haven't gotten bored with,</font>

462
00:21:38,510 --> 00:21:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I have no plans to quit.</font>

463
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all a bunch of weirdos.</font>

464
00:21:47,860 --> 00:21:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san! Did you just smile?</font>

465
00:21:50,730 --> 00:21:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not smiling.</font>

466
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:52,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

467
00:21:52,930 --> 00:21:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the first time I've seen it!</font>

468
00:21:54,910 --> 00:21:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too.</font>

469
00:21:56,090 --> 00:21:57,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't seen it much, either!</font>

470
00:21:59,370 --> 00:22:01,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should smile more!</font>

471
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up.</font>

472
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:04,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hurry up and grab a bath, 
then get some food.</font>

473
00:22:04,450 --> 00:22:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure thing.</font>

474
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

